  "notes": "The main underground floor connecting all four entrance caves and giving access to B2F. B1F is the largest map in the complex at 20x18 blocks (40x36 tiles). It receives 6 staircases from the four entrance caves and has 9 total warp connections: NW (5,5), NE-far (35,3), NE-near (29,9), SW-west (9,31), SW-east (23,31), SE (31,29), two descents to B2F at (25,21) and (13,27), and a passage to WhirlIslandCave at (17,21). Items: 5 visible item balls (Full Restore, Carbos, Calcium, Nugget, Escape Rope) plus 3 hidden items (Rare Candy, Ultra Ball, Full Restore). One Strength Boulder at (23,26) blocks lower path. Wild encounters are level 23-26, one tier above entrance caves. Source: maps/WhirlIslandB1F.asm, constants/map_constants.asm line 136, data/wild/johto_grass.asm lines 985-1011."
